{"tid":2514368,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"跟銀行假就冇得補假？","createTime":"2021-05-03T08:21:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T08:49:21.000Z","uid":53312,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2bf5a41f083bd5da73544f08256abc0400e867dc","tid":2514368,"uid":53312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:21:54.000Z","msg":"借朋友ac一用<br />\n<br />\n是咁的！我係一個禮拜放1日假，放星期六唔係放星期日<br />\n咁啱撞正5月1日係星期六，咁我上網見勞工法例話如果休息日撞正公眾假期就應該要補假俾員工，咁我就問公司係咪會補假俾我啦！<br />\n<br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 因為我一個禮拜係放一日，咁星期六應該算係我嘅例假，咁啱撞正5月1日，公司係咪應該補假俾我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 我地放嘅係銀行假，有17日假期俾你，唔係放勞工假，我上勞工處網站見到勞工假係法定假先有得補，你咁樣係冇得補假俾你，如果你有得補假，咁我放星六，日嘅員工咪全部都可以補多日假囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 但我見月曆上星期日撞到公眾假期都有得補假，咁我星期日要返工，唔係應該當我星期六放假係星期日咁補返日俾我咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 月曆上寫嘅係補假係政府俾你，唔慣我地公司事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 如果咁計，萬一返shift嘅員工，佢一星期放得1日，咁老闆將佢嘅休息日全部放係紅日到，咁果位員工咪一世都冇得補假囉(咁銀行假咪即係廢)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 係㗎，總之放銀行假就得補，勞工假先得，你係咪想改做放勞工假？咁我就可以補俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n打俾勞工處電話冇人聽，想聽下各位意見係點，依家覺得好無助，係咪真係冇得補假<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8e3a4ea5dce35249b52bdae65ae6c57a6ffc431","tid":2514368,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:29:04.000Z","msg":"如果法定假日適逢僱員的休息日，僱主是否須要另外補假？<br />\n 須要。如法定假日適逢僱員的休息日，僱主應於休息日翌日補假。該補假須並非法定假日，另定假日，代替假日或休息日的日子。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/faq/cap57f_whole.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.labour.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Ffaq%2Fcap57f_whole.htm&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOIGpPR2DWAUw81xbwDiv9SI%3D&h=c2ca33b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/faq/cap57f_whole.htm</a>"},{"pid":"7fb47416a2276e091654260f97bd2424fcae64ee","tid":2514368,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:29:50.000Z","msg":"俾條link老細叫佢收皮"},{"pid":"7a0aa0c101c581cd1c94bd576880e97ddd297343","tid":2514368,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:30:56.000Z","msg":"咁小家 搵定下一份啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d80e89a1036fa6dfefcd50eee13833ff0bd26fbf","tid":2514368,"uid":50423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:31:45.000Z","msg":"樓主6天工作? 好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d64430023c90f4943b363d6653600e4e5f36f34","tid":2514368,"uid":53312,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b8e3a4ea5dce35249b52bdae65ae6c57a6ffc431","tid":2514368,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:29:04.000Z","msg":"如果法定假日適逢僱員的休息日，僱主是否須要另外補假？<br />\n 須要。如法定假日適逢僱員的休息日，僱主應於休息日翌日補假。該補假須並非法定假日，另定假日，代替假日或休息日的日子。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/faq/cap57f_whole.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.labour.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Ffaq%2Fcap57f_whole.htm&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOIGpPR2DWAUw81xbwDiv9SI%3D&h=c2ca33b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/faq/cap57f_whole.htm</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:40:57.000Z","msg":"我有咁俾公司啲人睇<br />\n佢話我放嘅係叫做銀行假，並非勞工假，勞工假先係法定假期有得補，銀行假就唔會有得補，佢仲話如果我真係要補假就不如跟勞工假咁放，以後就少5日假咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d2d26c0431481bb2b4d2bc6772d2c38981457b4","tid":2514368,"uid":53312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d80e89a1036fa6dfefcd50eee13833ff0bd26fbf","tid":2514368,"uid":50423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:31:45.000Z","msg":"樓主6天工作? 好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:43:48.000Z","msg":"係呀，鬼叫我低學歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5081d67d800d5b1b319308a1b1046b90bfc90c86","tid":2514368,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:49:21.000Z","msg":"大鳩你公司咪佢做乜鳩啦<br />\n如果放假個日撞正紅日要補假架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}